   {
      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "@pstratem what's the best way to handle this situation? If the getblocktemplate call from the scheduled poll returns an updated template it will get pushed out to miners anyways(shouldn't bitcoind be interrupting CNB and rerunning it if a new block comes in?), I thought CNB is single threaded and that doing simultaneous getblocktemplate calls would not make the second return any faster.\n",
      "created_at" : "2015-11-27T07:30:34Z",
      "html_url" : "https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/7104#issuecomment-160058799",
